member.name: SERVERCALL
member.summary: Indicates the status of server call.

member.name: SERVERCALL.SERVERCALL_ISHANDLED
member.summary: The object may be able to process the call.

member.name: SERVERCALL.SERVERCALL_REJECTED
member.summary: The object cannot handle the call due to an unforeseen problem, such as network unavailability.

member.name: SERVERCALL.SERVERCALL_RETRYLATER
member.summary: The object cannot handle the call at this time. For example, an application might return this value when it is in a user-controlled modal state.
